Hindusthan National Glass Says Company Secretary Resigns

-- B y   A b h i s h e k   S h a n k e r
-- 
2011-09-15T13:56:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/hindusthan-national-glass-says-company-secretary-resigns.html
Hindusthan National Glass &
Industries Ltd., a maker of glass bottles, today said both the
company secretary and the compliance officer have resigned from
the company and they have been relieved of their services from
Sept. 10, according to an exchange filing.             To contact the reporter on this story:
